    14→/// This database manages all local data storage for the SoloAdventurer app,
    15→/// including trips, journals, users, and synchronization queue.
    16→///
    17→/// The database follows these principles:
    18→/// - **Type Safety**: Uses Drift's compile-time checked queries
    19→/// - **Offline-First**: All data is stored locally and synced with the server
    20→/// - **Sync Tracking**: Every data table includes fields for sync state
    21→/// - **Conflict Resolution**: Version tracking enables conflict detection
